metadata.name: Mandeloculars - 02
metadata.description: [Mandeloculars AI](https://www.behance.net/gallery/151098405/Mandeloculars-AI) is a remake of my  [Mandeloculars](https://www.behance.net/gallery/3855759/Mandeloculars) series. Ten years have passed between the two series, the opportunity to measure the technical progress made in the meantime. Since then, AIs have become more efficient, the possibilities have changed. So I took the opportunity to revisit my series with this great new tool.
